(1877, 'Aurory-Moves-Things-up-a-Gear-with-a-Slew-of-Summer-Updates', 'Aurory Moves Things up a Gear with a Slew of Summer Updates', 'Outstanding Solana based NFT RPG romp, Aurory, has unveiled a series of incredible updates making a beeline for its… The post Aurory Moves Things up a Gear with a Slew of Summer Updates appeared first on NFT Plazas.', 'Outstanding Solana based NFT RPG romp, Aurory , has unveiled a series of incredible updates making a beeline for its well-polished platform this summer. In the near future, gamers will see the project go cross chain, engage with stunning new art, and witness the game hub get a shiny new revamp. Since the NFT market got a little shaky, some NFT gaming companies have remained in perpetual development. Seemingly waiting for the opportune moment to launch their titles while the going is hot, and crypto is once again the talk of the town. Not Aurory however, which, come rain or shine has continued soldiering on with its flagship platform, regardless of the market climate, or the mad rumblings of crypto Twitter. Through this constant drive to innovate and engage, Aurory has risen as a powerhouse in NFT gaming. One that effectively now stands on its own merit and is not held up by the pillars of market volatility. So, it’s not unexpected then, that while traditional NFT projects like Azuki are up in flames , Aurory has unveiled a series of magnificent updates. Aurory to Travel Beyond its Familiar Solana Surroundings Part of Aurory’s intriguing round of platform enhancements will see it travel beyond the confines of its Solana home. So far, the team has remained tight lipped with regards to the specific network it will engage with. However, wheat we do know is it will exist on the Ethereum Virtual Machine, and launch some time in July. What’s more, Aurory has also revealed that it will also cross the threshold of traditional gaming by merging with some legacy Web2 platforms. Effectively, broadening its reach to encompass the many facets of the video gaming community. In addition to these major milestones, the Aurory team has announced a major upgrade to its NFT artwork, with an option for holders to upgrade their character. While a new game hub and customization feature for ‘non-Aurorians’ is also on the cards. Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas Join the Weekly Newsletter Follow us on Twitter Like us on Facebook Follow us on Instagram *All investment/financial opinions expressed by NFT Plazas are from the personal research and experience of our site moderators and are intended as educational material only. Individuals are required to fully research any product prior to making any kind of investment.', NULL, NULL, 'https://nftplazas.com/aurory-summer-updates/', '2023-07-07 00:30:53', 'united kingdom', NULL, '2023-07-07 08:18:42', '2023-07-07 08:18:42', 2, 'NFT Gaming News;Aurory', NULL, 0),
(1878, 'What-is-LUKSO-and-How-to-add-LUKSO-to-Metamask', 'What is LUKSO and How to add LUKSO to Metamask?', 'LUKSO is a trailblazing EVM blockchain. his guide will simplify your life by demonstrating how to add LUKSO to MetaMask wallet.', 'In the evolving world of cryptocurrencies, it’s crucial to keep your digital wallets up-to-date with the latest blockchain networks. This guide will simplify your life by demonstrating how to add LUKSO to MetaMask wallet . Contenu 1 What is LUKSO? 2 LUKSO Standards Proposals (LSPs): The Foundation of LUKSO Ecosystem 3 Universal Profiles: Revolutionizing Digital Identity 4 LSP6 Key Manager and Advanced Access 5 Facilitating Creative Economies with Identifiable Digital Assets and NFTs 6 LSP6 Key Manager and the Future of Transaction Relay Services 7 ERC725 Standard: The Foundation of Multiple LSPs 8 LUKSO’s Sustainable Future: Embracing Proof of Stake 9 Why Add LUKSO to MetaMask? 10 How to add LUKSO to MetaMask: Step-by-Step Guide 10.1 Step 1: Open MetaMask Dropdown Menu 10.2 Step 2: Navigate to “Add Network” 10.3 Step 3: Manually Add the Network 10.4 Step 4: Enter LUKSO Network Information 10.5 Step 5: Confirm and Explore 11 Wrapping Up What is LUKSO? LUKSO is a trailblazing EVM blockchain, rooted in the Casper PoS architecture, set to transform the interaction between brands, creators, and users within blockchain technology in the emerging Creative Economy. It’s the brainchild of Fabian Vogelsteller and Marjorie Hernandez, who are recognized innovators in their respective fields. Fabian Vogelsteller, a key contributor to Ethereum as a lead DApp developer, is renowned for authoring both ERC20 and web3.js, the pivotal elements of contemporary DeFi and NFT protocols. Marjorie Hernandez, an expert in innovation and product development, was instrumental in founding and managing EY’s Digital Innovation Lab in Berlin. LUKSO Standards Proposals (LSPs): The Foundation of LUKSO Ecosystem The initial LUKSO Standards Proposals (LSPs) form the structural basis of the LUKSO ecosystem. They strive to enhance functionality and ease-of-use within the blockchain ecosystem while standardizing facets like identity, asset depiction, and smart contract transactions. The fundamental LSPs are highly adaptable, paving the way for a myriad of new applications and simplifying both developer and user experiences. These standards are ‘neutral,’ indicating their broad-based application that fosters the emergence of yet unconceived use cases. Universal Profiles: Revolutionizing Digital Identity Universal Profiles are interoperable blockchain-based identities that enable verifiable identities in the digital realm. These profiles offer a universal login system that eliminates the need for traditional usernames and passwords, providing full control over all your virtual assets and identity. They streamline the onboarding process to Web3 for users, brands, and creators, enhancing accessibility, security, and functionality. LSP6 Key Manager and Advanced Access The LSP6 Key Manager enables the addition of varied access levels, inclusive of dApp access and other environments. Universal Profiles enhance on-chain security for users, enabling users to react to received assets/tokens, such as rejecting transfers, via the LSP1 Universal Receiver. Facilitating Creative Economies with Identifiable Digital Assets and NFTs Universal profiles facilitate economic and verifiable interactions, serving as the cornerstone for the new creative economies. The LSP8 Identifiable Digital Asset and LSP7 Digital Asset NFT allow for highly extensible and smart contract-readable token metadata inputs. These metadata inputs can evolve over time, enabling post-minting modification of NFTs. On LUKSO, NFTs and tokens can have multiple creators and inform receivers of assets, making complex smart contract automation possible. LSP6 Key Manager and the Future of Transaction Relay Services Co-founder Fabian Vogelsteller proposed the ERC725 smart contract standard in 2017 to establish a blockchain-based account system. The LSP6 Key Manager enables relay transactions, allowing third parties to cover a user’s transaction fees (GAS). Recommended posts PEPE Coin Price to Reach $5 in the Next Seven Days? To the article Universal Profiles can work with any future transaction relay service. As relay services are backend systems executing user transactions, users don’t need initial funds to use their Universal Profiles. LUKSO plans to support early adopters by providing a public relay service, simplifying interactions with the LUKSO blockchain. ERC725 Standard: The Foundation of Multiple LSPs The ERC725 standard serves as the foundation for any entity requiring public, verifiable storage of its information, as well as executing arbitrary smart contracts. This standard underpins numerous LSPs, enhancing the functionality of tokens, NFTs, and forming the core standard of Universal Profiles. LUKSO’s Sustainable Future: Embracing Proof of Stake LUKSO operates on a Proof of Stake (PoS) blockchain model, which is markedly more energy-efficient than Proof of Work (PoW) models, utilizing 99% less energy as it eliminates the need for competitive hash generation to reach consensus on the latest canonical block head. Why Add LUKSO to MetaMask? As a blockchain dedicated to digital lifestyles and economies, LUKSO offers a unique environment for creators, consumers, and developers. Adding it to MetaMask not only extends your reach within the blockchain sphere, it also enhances your ability to interact with various digital assets. How to add LUKSO to MetaMask: Step-by-Step Guide This detailed explanation is derived from and inspired by the insightful information shared in this Twitter thread . The objective is to simplify the complexities and provide a broad overview for better understanding. Step 1: Open MetaMask Dropdown Menu To start, you need to open your MetaMask (MM) wallet. Look for the arrow dropdown menu that reveals the list of networks you have connected to your wallet. Step 2: Navigate to “Add Network” Once you have the network list open, scroll down to the end of the list. You will find an “Add Network” button. Click on it to add a new network. Step 3: Manually Add the Network After clicking “Add Network”, a new page will appear with several fields to fill out. Here, you should select “Add a network manually”. Step 4: Enter LUKSO Network Information This is the crucial step that requires the correct information about the LUKSO network. You will find this information in the LUKSO documentation . Enter the necessary data exactly as it appears in the documentation, as mistakes may result in the network not connecting properly. Step 5: Confirm and Explore Once all the necessary information is filled out, confirm by clicking the ‘Save’ button. Now, LUKSO will appear as an available network in your MetaMask dropdown list. You can easily switch to the LUKSO network and explore the blockchain to ensure it has linked correctly. Wrapping Up With this guide, adding LUKSO to your MetaMask becomes an effortless task. Being a part of the LUKSO network will grant you the opportunity to interact with various tokens ($LYX, $LYXE), and engage with a whole new universe of digital possibilities. Don’t forget to check back often for more updates on how to maximize your MetaMask wallet! Recommended posts PEPE Coin Price to Reach $5 in the Next Seven Days? Shiba Inu Price Prediction: How High can SHIB Price reach by 2030? Can Shiba Inu Price Reach 10 Cents? SHIB’s Burn Rate Soars: Can it Ignite a Price Rally in 2023? Shiba Inu to Reach 1$ soon? This New Upcoming Development Proves it Right Big News: Ripple Price is about to TRIPLE? This News Confirms… The Big Ripple Price Prediction for 2023 – How high can the XRP price go in 2023? Shiba Inu Price Prediction – Shib Price is Up, Will it Continue to Climb? Ripple Price Prediction – How High will XRP Reach in 2025? Ripple Price Prediction – How High will XRP reach in 