(1983, '\'SA-to-the-world\':-Jay-Z-spotted-listening-to-Amapiano-in-his-car', '‘SA to the world’: Jay Z spotted listening to Amapiano in his car', 'American rapper Jay Z has been spotted listening to an Amapiano song in his car at Michael Rubin\'s exclusive all white party.', 'American rapper Shawn Corey Carter, popularly known as Jay-Z, was spotted listening to an Amapiano song in his Landrove at Michael Rubin’s exclusive all white party, as seen in a recent video that surfaced on social media on 4 July. In a recent video that has surfaced on social media, Jay Z is seen jamming to the Amapiano song “Monalisa” by Lojays and Sarz. The video was taken as Jay Z and his friends pulled up in his Landrover, arriving to attend Michael Rubin’s exclusive all white party in the Hamptons. ALSO READ: ‘Blue Ivy’s bro’: SA tweeps insist Kelly Rowland had Jay Z’s baby Michael Rubin’s Star studded party For three years in a row, businessman and philanthropist Michael Rubin together with his partner Camille Fischel have hosted their much talked about exclusive white party. This year their star studded event took place at their home in the Hamptons in celebration of the Fourth of July. The event saw the attendance of celebs like Jay Z, Beyoncé, Kelly Rowland, Kim Kardashian, Kendall Jenner, Kevin Hart, Leonardo DiCaprio, Jennifer Lopez, Ben Affleck, Dj Khaled, Travis Scott and Justin Bieber just to name a few. ALSO READ: Inside Beyoncé and Jay-Z’s R1.6 billion Bel-Air mansion [photos] Amapiano to the world Over the last three years Amapiano has rapidly taken over the world. From global trending Amapiano dance challenges, to the welcoming reception, it’s evident that Amapiano is here to stay! So much so that artists like Jay Z seem to have taken an interest in the genre. Recently Uncle Waffles was spotted with Kelly Rowland after performing at Coachella. Not to mention Drake just announced that Kabza De Small will be producing his new up and coming concert. Similarly, the Amapiano genre has introduced a plethora of newer artists to the world. ALSO READ: Eish! Cassper Nyovest’s ‘baby mama’ fails Amapiano dance routine CLICK HERE TO READ MORE ARTICLES BY WANIQUE BLOCK', 'https://www.thesouthafrican.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Untitled-design-1-1.png', NULL, 'https://www.thesouthafrican.com/lifestyle/celeb-news/jay-z-spotted-listening-to-amapiano-in-his-car-7-july-2023/', '2023-07-07 05:18:56', 'south africa', NULL, '2023-07-07 11:30:01', '2023-07-07 11:30:01', 2, 'Celeb News;amapiano;Beyonce;Featured;jay z', NULL, 0),
(1984, 'Police-need-help-identifying-one-of-the-bodies-connected-to-Bester\'s-escape', 'Police need help identifying one of the bodies connected to Bester’s escape', 'The police need help identifying one of the bodies meant to be used in Bester\'s escape – it was recovered from the Modder River earlier this year.', 'One of the bodies meant to be used in Thabo Bester’s escape is yet to be identified. The Free State police are turning to the public to help locate the man’s family. READ: ‘Thriving black market for seal meat’: Suspect arrested in Cape Town BODY CLAIMED BY BESTER ACCOMPLICE NEEDS TO BE IDENTIFIED The body was recovered twice. First, it was found in Lovedale Road, Bloemfontein, after a hit-and-run incident on 9 October 2021. “The body was then claimed by one of the suspects in the Thabo Bester Escape case at the Bloemfontein Government Mortuary,” said South African Police Service (SAPS) spokesperson Brigadier Motantsi Makhele. READ: Worst in drivers in the world: SA ranked last in fatal accident index The body was found for the second time in the Modder River on April 2022 – weeks before Bester escaped from the Mangaung Correctional Centre (MCC) after faking his death. Bester’s lover, Nandipha Magudumana, got hold of three bodies from Bloemfontein morgues. One of these was smuggled into a prison cell and set alight. The police believe the burnt body is that of Katlego Mpholo. READ: Chilly conditions ahead: Strong cold front to bring temperature drop to SA Bester escaped from the MCC in May 2022, and was recaptured earlier this year. Twelve suspects, including the man himself, have been charged for their alleged involvement in the escape. Bester was serving a life sentence plus 75 years for rape and murder at the time of his escape. Members of the public who can help identify the man’s body or locate his next of kin are encouraged to contact Colonel Ben Bolsiek at 082-466-8530. READ: ‘Very sad morning’: Ramaphosa urges investigators to uncover what caused fatal gas leak 📣 Join the Conversation: Comment below and share your thoughts 🗣️ CLICK HERE TO READ MORE ARTICLES BY STORM SIMPSON', 'https://www.thesouthafrican.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Untitled-design-2023-07-07T123331.460.jpg.optimal.jpg', NULL, 'https://www.thesouthafrican.com/news/unidentified-body-thabo-bester-escape-public-help-modder-river-7-june-2023/', '2023-07-07 05:16:51', 'south africa', NULL, '2023-07-07 11:30:01', '2023-07-07 11:30:01', 2, 'News;crime;Featured;Important;Thabo Bester', NULL, 0),
(1985, 'Kraken\'s-Jesse-Powell-under-federal-investigation-but-exchange-remains-uninvolved', 'Kraken’s Jesse Powell under federal investigation but exchange remains uninvolved', 'Crypto exchange Kraken told CryptoSlate it is not part of the current federal investigations into its co-founder Jesse Powell, according to a July 7 press statement. Powell is the subject of Federal Investigations. Powell is currently involved in a civil dispute with the Verge Center for the Arts, a non-profit art gallery. This news was […] The post Kraken’s Jesse Powell under federal investigation but exchange remains uninvolved appeared first on CryptoSlate.', 'Share Tweet Post Share Post Email Crypto exchange Kraken told CryptoSlate it is not part of the current federal investigations into its co-founder Jesse Powell , according to a July 7 press statement. Powell is the subject of Federal Investigations. Powell is currently involved in a civil dispute with the Verge Center for the Arts, a non-profit art gallery. This news was confirmed to CryptoSlate by people familiar with the matter. The dispute revolves around allegations made by Powell, who claims that Verge improperly removed him from its Board of directors and subsequently accused him of unauthorized access to its email system following his dismissal. The news was first reported by the New York Times . Kraken is aware of the investigations. A Kraken spokesperson confirmed to CryptoSlate that the exchange was aware of the federal investigations. “We understand there is a federal investigation open and search warrants were executed to gather more information about the Verge matter.” In its press statement, a Kraken spokesperson said the firm was not implicated in the ongoing investigation, nor does the investigation pertain to Powell’s former role at the exchange. The spokesperson said: “The US Attorney has advised us that Kraken is not a part of the investigation in any way, and the investigation does not concern Jesse’s affiliation with Kraken.” Powell is Kraken’s co-founder and was the company’s CEO until April when he transitioned to a non-executive role as the chairman of the exchange’s Board. Dave Ripley succeeded Powell as Kraken’s CEO. Posted In: Kraken , U.S. , Exchanges , Legal Author Oluwapelumi Adejumo Journalist at CryptoSlate Oluwapelumi values Bitcoin\'s potential. He imparts insights on a range of topics like DeFi, hacks, mining and culture, underlining transformative power. Editor Liam \'Akiba\' Wright Senior Editor at CryptoSlate Also known as \"Akiba,\" Liam is a reporter, editor and podcast producer at CryptoSlate. He believes that decentralized technology has the potential to make widespread positive change. Latest Kraken Stories Kraken says it fought IRS to protect clients against identity theft, other potential harms Taxes 4 days ago 1 min read Kraken ordered to provide IRS with user data Legal 6 days ago 2 min read Dave Ripley takes over as Kraken CEO, set on next phase of growth and expansion People 2 months ago 1 min read Press Releases // View All Advertise Here Nayms Issues World’s First Crypto-Denominated Industry Loss Warranty (ILW) Chainwire 10 hours ago Tether launches USDt on Kava Chainwire 11 hours ago Nexo Attains Type 2 SOC 2 Audit, Affirming Data Security Compliance News Desk 20 hours ago Disclaimer: Our writers\' opinions are solely their own and do not reflect the opinion of CryptoSlate. None of the information you read on CryptoSlate should be taken as investment advice, nor does CryptoSlate endorse any project that may be mentioned or linked to in this article. Buying and trading cryptocurrencies should be considered a high-risk activity. Please do your own due diligence before taking any action related to content within this article. Finally, CryptoSlate takes no responsibility should you lose money trading cryptocurrencies.', NULL, NULL, 'https://cryptoslate.com/krakens-jesse-powell-under-federal-investigation-but-exchange-remains-uninvolved/', '2023-