fe. Prepare yourself for a much-needed relief from the long-standing tensions and burdens of life. Now is the opportune moment to make lasting lifestyle changes that will keep these worries at bay permanently. The arrival of money today will alleviate many of your financial troubles, bringing a sense of relief. Friends will extend invitations for an enjoyable evening at their place. Ensure you maintain your best behavior, as your lover may display a highly unpredictable mood. During the day, you may stumble upon an old item in your house that triggers nostalgic memories of your childhood days. It can be a sentimental and heartwarming experience. Initially, you may feel uneasy about an action taken by your spouse, but later you will realize it was for the best. However, be prepared for some disappointment from someone close to you today. Lucky Colour: Yellow. Auspicious Time: 7 pm to 8 pm. As a remedy, store water in a green-colored glass bottle and expose it to the sun. This practice is believed to bring abundant happiness to your family members. Take extra care of your health, especially if you are dealing with high blood pressure. It is advisable to seek proper advice before making any investments. Later in the day, expect unexpected good news that will bring happiness and joy to the entire family. Your sweetheart will prove to be an angel for you today, provided you share love and affection. Although you will attempt to dedicate your time to your beloved, some important work may prevent you from doing so. Today, after a considerable period of time, you will receive a warm and comforting embrace from your spouse, creating a sense of coziness. When spending more time than usual with your family, there is a possibility of friction arising. It is recommended to actively avoid any potential conflicts today. Lucky Colour: Green. Auspicious Time: 5 pm to 7 pm. As a remedy, consider distributing rice pudding to little girls as it is believed to bring happiness and contentment. Expectant mothers can look forward to a day of special care dedicated to them. Today, there is a possibility of receiving financial benefits in business or employment with the assistance of a person of the opposite sex. It will be a delightful time spent with loved ones, as you strive to make your life more meaningful by finding joy and practicing forgiveness for past mistakes. Students are advised to prioritize their studies and avoid wasting time socializing with friends. This phase of their academic journey is crucial for progress and future success. It is common knowledge that hugs have numerous health benefits, and today, you can expect to receive plenty of them from your spouse. However, it’s important to brace yourself for potential bad news early in the day, as it has the potential to negatively impact the remainder of your day. Therefore, it is advisable to maintain control over your emotions. Lucky Colour: Green. Auspicious Time: 10.30 am to 12 pm. Remedy: Try keeping a green-colored glass bottle under the sun and mix the water from it with your bathing water, as it is believed to contribute to a disease-free life. Your compassionate and giving nature can be a hidden blessing, as it has the potential to free you from negative qualities such as uncertainty, disloyalty, sadness, lack of faith, greed, attachment, egoism, and jealousy. Today, profitable opportunities in business have the potential to bring happiness to numerous traders and entrepreneurs. However, tensions may arise within the family or with your spouse, but you will find solace in the loving embrace of your beloved. Engaging in seminars and exhibitions will provide you with valuable knowledge and new connections. It’s important to be aware that conflicts within the family could impact your married life. Additionally, excessive workload at the office today may lead to eye-related issues. Lucky Colour: Pink. Auspicious Time: 3 pm to 4.30 pm. Remedy: Consider nurturing white plants in your