(2772, 'Viral-Video:-78-year-old-man-proposes-school-crush-at-airport-Netizens-are-in-awe', 'Viral Video: 78-year-old man proposes school crush at airport, Netizens are in awe', 'If you are in love with someone, it’s never late to confession to that person. Such a video of a senior man proposing his school crush after 60 years in an airport is going viral in internet. The 78-year-old man was seen kneeling and asking his lady love to marry him. In the heartwarming video, […] The post Viral Video: 78-year-old man proposes school crush at airport, Netizens are in awe appeared first on KalingaTV.', 'If you are in love with someone, it’s never late to confession to that person. Such a video of a senior man proposing his school crush after 60 years in an airport is going viral in internet. The 78-year-old man was seen kneeling and asking his lady love to marry him. In the heartwarming video, Thomas, a medical professional from Tampa, was seen proposing to his high school crush Nancy at an airport. In the beginning, the elderly man was seen waiting for his lady love to arrive. The moment she reached, Thomas goes in for a warm hug and directs her to a seat. As she settled down, the man got down on both the knees and proposed her to marry him. Nancy immediately responded with a ‘yes’. The heart touching video has been shared on Instagram by an account known as Magically News. The viral video has been shared with a caption, “A love story 60 years in the making, when Dr. Thomas got down on one knee at Tampa International Airport to give his now fiancé, Nancy, a fairy-tale ending she’ll cherish forever.” The video has so far gained nearly 8.3 lakh views so far. Netizens are in awe after watching the video. On commented, “Rare to see a man his age not proposing to a woman young enough to be his daughter, He’s a gem.” While another wrote, “He’s on both knees lol. He meant that.” At the same time third user commented, “Such a Sterling example of a man’s love to a woman who deserves it.” Netizens have appreciated the video a lot as the elderly sets an example that true love does not care about age. Prev News Next News', NULL, NULL, 'https://kalingatv.com/offbeat/viral-video-78-year-old-man-proposes-school-crush-at-airport-netizens-are-in-awe/', '2023-07-10 02:36:25', 'india', NULL, '2023-07-10 08:30:01', '2023-07-10 08:30:01', 2, 'Offbeat;OffBeat;Viral video', '', 0),
