(4000, 'Dua-Lipa\'s-Steamy-Bathroom-Selfie-Has-Fans-Doing-Double-Takes', 'Dua Lipa’s Steamy Bathroom Selfie Has Fans Doing Double Takes', '247 News Around The World 247 News Around The World Dua Lipa recently shared a photo that sparked speculation and intrigue among… The post Dua Lipa’s Steamy Bathroom Selfie Has Fans Doing Double Takes appeared first on 247 News Around The World.', 'Dua Lipa recently shared a photo that sparked speculation and intrigue among fans regarding her love life. The shot, which was taken in the singer’s bathroom, revealed a detail that seemed to suggest she was having sex prior to taking the picture. Lipa is currently in a relationship with filmmaker Romain Gavras, whom she was linked with in February. The duo went public with their relationship in May during their appearance at the Cannes Film Festival. The singer celebrated Gavras’s birthday on her Instagram page two months later. Keep on reading to learn more. Dua Lipa’s Racy Photo Causes A Buzz Online MEGA Dua Lipa sparked a significant buzz on social media when she shared a bathroom selfie that appeared to include a racy element . For the shot, she was dressed in a large gray t-shirt, accessorized with gold earrings and a necklace. Lipa also pulled up the outfit to reveal her black lace pants, flat tummy, and some parts of her legs. While many fans admired Lipa’s beauty in the photo, some shifted their attention to the background. This Dua Lipa mirror selfie pic.twitter.com/mH2v1zwUAR — nainiii 🧜‍♀️ (@lipathingz) July 5, 2023 They zeroed in on what appeared to be handprints on the steam-covered glass door of the bathroom and speculated that Lipa had engaged in a steamy sex session before posing for the picture. One fan made a saucy comment that read , “From what I’m seeing something really happened on that shower.” Another mentioned , “There was nothing clean going on in that shower from what I see.” A third fan asked , “Wonder what she was doing inside that shower?” while a fourth wrote , “[We] all seeing them hand prints back there,” with a smiley face emoji. Dua Lipa’s Vacation With Boyfriend Romain Gavras A few days ago, Lipa shared more sultry shots of herself, which she took during a getaway with her boyfriend, French filmmaker Gavras. The couple was visiting the Greek Island of Sifnos, as noted in the caption she added to the carousel of images. In two of the shots, the “Don’t Start Now” singer was seen wearing a sexy black two-piece bikini. One of them featured her paddling a surfboard, while she showed off her tan in the other image while posing on a boat against scenic cliffs. In a third image, Lipa showcased her dance moves in a vibrant lime green outfit with neon lights as the backdrop. A fourth photo captured her in a black sequin dress, holding a woven bag. Additionally, a romantic moment between Lipa and Gavras was captured in front of a traditional Greek house, with both of them dressed in matching black attire. The Pair Were First Linked In February Instagram | Dua Lipa Speculations about a romantic involvement between the “Don’t Start Now” singer and French filmmaker emerged in February when they were seen leaving a BAFTA afterparty together, per People magazine. The following month, they were pictured with their hands intertwined as they left Saint Laurent’s Paris Fashion Week show. From then on, occasional glimpses of Gavras were seen on Lipa’s Instagram page, including a picture of themselves from her vacation in Jamaica. On May 19, Gavras and Lipa made their relationship public at the Cannes Film Festival. They attended the premiere of “Omar La Fraise” and were photographed on the red carpet, with Gavras embracing Lipa as they posed for the cameras. Lipa wore an elegant black one-shoulder dress for the ceremony, while Gavras opted for a spiffy black suit and tie. Dua Lipa Celebrates Her Boyfriend’s Birthday Instagram | Dua Lipa Earlier in the month, Lipa posted a cute message to wish her boyfriend a happy birthday, along with a cute picture of themselves. Lipa was captured in the photo wearing a long-sleeved black and white polka-dot dress, strolling together with Gavras on a hotel balcony. Her partially visible face showed her directing a smile at the 42-year-old filmmaker while her arm was casually draped over his shoulder. Gavras, on the other hand, had his arms wrapped around Lipa, donning a white ribbed jacket and matching pants. He completed his ensemble with a stylish cap and sneakers. She captioned the shot in French, “Joyeux anniversaireeeee bébé,” which translates to Happy Birthday Baby. She also added the revolving hearts emoji to further express her affection for him. Post source: The blast', NULL, NULL, 'https://247newsaroundtheworld.com/news/dua-lipas-steamy-bathroom-selfie-has-fans-doing-double-takes/', '2023-07-10 04:06:22', 'united kingdom', NULL, '2023-07-10 10:30:01', '2023-07-10 10:30:01', 2, 'News', '', 0),
